data.description: Hilldale School District, Wonderful brick home with a fireplace sitting up on a corner lot and in great condition, ready for a new family.  There are beautiful counter tops, and appliances and spacious rooms.  Come take a look at this three bedroom two bath home. The backyard is huge and is totally fenced with privacy fencing.  This home should finance FHA, VA or Sec 184. Call for a private showing.
